  "texts": [
    "[259] -FT, AT, PE Stable diffusion X-ray images, Text CMR Qilin-Med-VL [260] -FT, AT, PE CLIP-ViT+Chinese-LLaMA Multimodal images, Text VQA PathAsst [261] -FT, AT PLIP-ViT+Vicuna Pathology images, Text CLS, DET, SEG, CMR, CMG PathChat [262] -FT, AT CONCH-ViT+LLaMA-2 Pathology images, Text VQA Lu et al. [263] -FT, AT ResNet+GPT/OpenLLaMA X-ray images, Text RG M 3 AD [264] -AT M 3 AE Multimodal images, Text VQA I-AI [265] -AT BiomedCLIP X-ray images, Text GMG, CLS CITE [266] -AT, PE CLIP-ViT+BioLinkBERT Pathology images, Text CLS XrayGPT [267] -AT, PE MedCLIP+Vicuna X-ray images, Text VQA Xplainer [268] -PE BioViL X-ray images, Text CLS Qin et al.",
    "[269] -PE GLIP Multimodal images, Text DET Guo et al. [270] -PE GLIP Multimodal images, Text DETgeneral-domain MFMs to the healthcare domain.",
    "For instance, CheXZero [253], PubMedCLIP [250], QUILTNET [254] and PLIP [255] are fine-tuned versions of CLIP [47] tailored for chest x-ray, radiology and histopathology.",
    "RoentGen [257] and [259] are medical domain-adapted latent diffusion models based on Stable Diffusion pipeline [21].",
    "LLaVA-Med [252], Med-Flamingo [251] and Med-PaLMM [31] followed LLaVA [274], Flamingo [275], and PaLM-E [276] with paired or interleaved medical image-text data."
  ]
